{
  "stem": "2067.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You will-- you will first have to be x-rayed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now, the nuns-- the nurses were all nuns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when I was taken to the x-ray laboratory, an old-fashioned thing, she said to me, you lie down now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I have to go outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And you lie still.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "As soon as she turned around to leave the room, I twisted my diaphragm so that one leg was shorter than the other.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they took the x-rays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He came in, the lieutenant, next morning, and said, let me measure your-- your two legs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He measured.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he found that the left that was two centimeters shorter than the right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "How that is, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But that's what he found.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "A day later, I was called to the-- to the room of the director and several other doctors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I spoke only French, and didn't let on that I understood every single word.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I heard the director, who was a colonel, say, I think this guy is faking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I'm going to ask him to walk up and down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Let's see how he gets up from the chair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Well, I faked it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "With difficulty, I got up and walked, of course, limping.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Then he said, tell him to-- to-- a priest was there as a-- as a--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--interpreter The priest said to me, the director wants you to lie down on that thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I climbed-- I climbed up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he tried to move my legs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I started yelling like crazy, and-- and held his hand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the lieutenant said, Colonel, you see that this man is in terrible pain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In short, it-- I succeeded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A day later, I was sent back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the priest, with a-- with a smile, said to me, you have nothing to worry.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
